data.description: Welcome to 170 Britts Dr, a stunning gem in the heart of Lenoir City, TN, where affordable luxury living meets spacious comfort. This all-brick, 4-bedroom, 2 full and 2 half bath residence boasts 2,927 square feet of living space and is nestled in the picturesque Rockingham subdivision.Situated on a desirable corner lot, this home exudes charm and curb appeal, welcoming you with its elegant facade and manicured landscaping. The Rockingham subdivision is known for its serene and lovely neighborhood, providing a peaceful retreat from the bustle of daily life while remaining conveniently close to major amenities.  Whether you need to commute, indulge in retail therapy, or seek medical care, it's all within easy reach, making this home perfect for the modern lifestyle.One of the standout features of this property is the master bedroom on the main level, offering a retreat within your own home. With ample space and privacy, you can unwind and relax in your personal sanctuary. The en-suite bathroom is a luxurious space, complete with modern amenities and elegant finishes, providing the perfect start and end to your day.The interior of this home is designed to impress, with an open layout, abundant natural light, and high-quality finishes. The spacious living areas and well-appointed kitchen create an inviting atmosphere for entertaining family and friends. The formal dining room is an ideal setting for special occasions and family gatherings.The outdoor living space is equally delightful, featuring a well-manicured yard, perfect for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the pleasant Tennessee weather. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee on the front porch or hosting a barbecue on the back patio, you'll appreciate the versatility of this corner lot.Contact me today to schedule your viewing and discover your future dream home.  All information deemed reliable, buyer to verify.
